<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c3">{بِمَوَاقِعِ النُّجُومِ}</span>: <span class="c1">" بِمُحْكَمِ القُرْآنِ،<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></span></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَيُقَالُ:</span> بِمَسْقِطِ النُّجُومِ إِذَا سَقَطْنَ،<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَمَوَاقِعُ , وَمَوْقِعٌ , وَاحِدٌ "<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>